  "system": {
    "biography": {
      "value": "<p>Ashwalkers stride into the middle of things and let their Heat Aura do supplementary work while their strikes deliver the primary punishment. They do not retreat. They have no concept of tactical withdrawal — they are fire, and fire does not back away from something that is not water. A Summoner who places one between allies and enemies and steps back will find it performs the job adequately until something wetter than expected shows up.</p>"
