    "attacksNotes": "<ul>\n<li><strong>Burning Strike [Combat]:</strong> Melee attack (Agi 5 + Melee Combat 4), Reach: 5 ft\n<ul>\n<li><em>Margin 1:</em> 6 damage + 4 fire damage (Half DR)</li>\n<li><em>Margin 2:</em> 10 damage (6 + 4 Str) + 4 fire damage; target gains Singed condition</li>\n<li><em>Margin 3:</em> 10 damage + 4 fire damage; target gains Ignited condition</li>\n</ul></li>\n</ul>",
